The paper deals with the problem of constructing straight-line drawings of a planar graph and its rectangular dual, which involves topics such as computational geometry (cs.CG), graph theory (cs.GT), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the resizing of the rectangular dual, which can be related to discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and optimization (cs.SI).
